column3: Examines the issues related to network based application development.
Techniques for web application penetration testing, secure software development techniques for network based applications.
Much of the work into security and privacy solutions ignore a critical element - the human who must interact with those solutions.
Introduction to the fundamentals of computer architectures and their programmability using assembly and system programming.
Matrix algebra, systems of linear equations, vector spaces, linear transformations, determinants, inner products, eigenvalues.
